```plantuml
@startuml Melacon_WirelessTransportEmulator

component "Docker Host" {
    component "Wireless Transport Emulator" as WTE {
        component "Topology Manager" as TM
        component "Configuration Manager" as CM
        component "Link Emulator" as LE
    }

    component "Network Elements (Docker Containers)" as NE {
        component "OpenYuma NETCONF Server" as OY
        component "YANG Models" as YM
        component "SIL (Server Instrumentation Layer)" as SIL
    }

    component "SDN Controller" as SDN
}

component "Management Station" as MS {
    component "yangcli" as CLI
    component "NETCONF Client" as NC
}

WTE --> NE : Manages\n(via Docker API)
WTE --> SDN : Reports topology\n(via REST API)
NE --> SDN : Exposes NETCONF\n(via SSH)
MS --> NE : NETCONF operations\n(via SSH)

TM -down-> CM : Reads config
CM -down-> LE : Configures links
OY --> YM : Validates against
OY --> SIL : Callbacks for\noperations
CLI --> OY : NETCONF commands
NC --> OY : NETCONF operations

@enduml
```